ign_and_accessibility\">設計與親合度</a></li>\n        </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n</ol>\n\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下連結會給出 HTML 常見待解問題的方法</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本結構","title":"基本結構","isH3":true,"content":"<p>HTML 文件的最基本結構應用。如果你是 HTML 新手，就先從這裡開始看。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/Getting_started#anatomy_of_an_html_document\">如何建立基本 HTML 文件</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/Document_and_website_structure\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">如何有邏輯地分割網頁 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/HTML_text_fundamentals#the_basics_headings_and_paragraphs\">如何建立良好的標題段落結構</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本文字語法","title":"基本文字語法","isH3":true,"content":"<p>HTML 專攻於為文件提供語義資訊，因此 HTML 可以提供使用者更精準的文件資訊傳達方式。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/HTML_text_fundamentals#lists\">如何建立清單</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/HTML_text_fundamentals#emphasis_and_importance\">如何強調文件的內容</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/HTML_text_fundamentals#emphasis_and_importance\">如何表示出一段文字的重要性</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/Advanced_text_formatting#representing_computer_code\">如何顯示程式碼</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Multimedia_and_embedding/Images_in_HTML#annotating_images_with_figures_and_figure_captions\">如何為圖片加入註記</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/Advanced_text_formatting#abbreviations\">如何標示並註記縮寫</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/Advanced_text_formatting#quotations\">如何在網頁中加入引用</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Define_terms_with_HTML\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">如何加入詞語的定義 (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"超連結","title":"超連結","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Hyperlink\">超連結 <small>(en-US)</small></a>把 HTML 導覽變得相當容易，它可以這麼用：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/Creating_hyperlinks\">如何建立超連結</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/Creating_hyperlinks#active_learning_creating_a_navigation_menu\">How to create a table of contents with HTML</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"圖片與多媒體","title":"圖片與多媒體","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Multimedia_and_embedding/Images_in_HTML#how_do_we_put_an_image_on_a_webpage\">How to add images to a webpage</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Multimedia_and_embedding/Video_and_audio_content\">How to add video content to a webpage</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Multimedia_and_embedding/Video_and_audio_content\">How to add audio content to a webpage</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"腳本與樣式","title":"腳本與樣式","isH3":true,"content":"<p>HTML 只建立文件的基礎架構，可以透過 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CSS\">CSS</a> 或腳本使內容呈現更具互動性。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/CSS/First_steps/How_CSS_works#how_to_apply_your_css_to_your_html\">如何在網頁中使用 CSS</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Use_JavaScript_within_a_webpage\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">如何在網頁中使用 JavaScript (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"嵌入內容","title":"嵌入內容","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Multimedia_and_embedding/Other_embedding_technologies\">How to embed a webpage within another webpage</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Multimedia_and_embedding/Other_embedding_technologies#the_<embed>_and_<object>_elements\">How to add Flash content within a webpage</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"不常見或進階的問題","title":"不常見或進階的問題","isH3":false,"content":"<p>除了上述的基本功能外，HTML 還提供許多進階功能讓使用者解決較複雜的問題。這些文章可以幫助你處理一些較不常見的情況：</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"表單","title":"表單","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Forms are a complex HTML structure made to send data from a webpage to a web server. We encourage you to go over our <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/Forms\">full dedicated guide</a>. Here is where you should start:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/Your_first_form\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">How to create a simple Web form (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/Forms/How_to_structure_a_web_form\">How to structure a Web form</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"表格訊息","title":"表格訊息","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Some information, called tabular data, needs to be organized into tables with columns and rows. It's one of the most complex HTML structures, and mastering it is not easy:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Create_a_data_spreadsheet\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">How to create a data spreadsheet</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Make_HTML_tables_accessible\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">How to make HTML tables accessible</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Optimize_HTML_table_rendering\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">How to optimize HTML table rendering</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"資料表示方式","title":"資料表示方式","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTMLHowto/Represent_numeric_values_with_HTML\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">How to represent numeric values with HTML</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Use_data_attributes\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">How to use data attributes (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Associate_human_readable_content_with_arbitrary_computer_data_structures\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">How to associate human readable content with arbitrary computer data structures</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"互動性","title":"互動性","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Create_collapsible_content_with_HTML\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">How to create collapsible content with HTML</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Add_context_menus_to_a_webpage\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">How to add context menus to a webpage</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Create_dialog_boxes_with_HTML\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">How to create dialog boxes with HTML</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"進階文字語法","title":"進階文字語法","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Take_control_of_HTML_line_breaking\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">How to take control of HTML line breaking</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Mark_text_insertion_and_deletion\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">How to mark changes (added and removed text)</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"進階圖片_多媒體","title":"進階圖片 &amp; 多媒體","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Multimedia_and_embedding/Responsive_images\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">How to add responsive image to a webpage (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Multimedia_and_embedding/Adding_vector_graphics_to_the_Web\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">How to add vector image to a webpage (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Add_a_hit_map_on_top_of_an_image\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">How to add a hit map on top of an image (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"進階圖片 & 多媒體"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"國際化","title":"國際化","isH3":true,"content":"<p>HTML is not monolingual. It provides tools to handle common internationalization issues.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Add_multiple_languages_into_a_single_webpage\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">How to add multiple languages into a single webpage</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Handle_Japanese_ruby_characters\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">How to handle Japanese ruby characters</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Display_time_and_date_with_HTML\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">How to display time and date with HTML</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"效能","title":"效能","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Author_fast-loading_HTML_pages\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">How to author fast-loading HTML pages (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"不常見或進階的問題","id":"不常見或進階的問題"}],"summary":"以下連結會給出 HTML 常見待解問題的方法","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Use HTML to solve common problems","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Solución de problemas comunes de HTML","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Apprendre à utiliser HTML pour résoudre des problèmes","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"一般的な問題解決に HTML を使う","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Learn HTML to solve problems","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Use HTML para resolver problemas comuns","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Использование HTML для решения общих задач","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"使用 HTML 解决常见问题","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/learn/html/howto","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/learn/html/howto/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Learn","title":"學習該如何開發 Web"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML","title":"學習 HTML ：指南與教學"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto","title":"使用HTML解決日常問題"}],"pageTitle":"使用HTML解決日常問題 - 學習該如何開發 Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}